title: Medic.ClueD
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
I've found this $CLUE. Know anything about it?
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Medic>>
<<Portrait|Medic_neutral>>
I'm busy right now, you should check in with $CREWMATE.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Thanks, Cerys.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Medic>>
<<Portrait|Medic_neutral>>
You are very welcome.
<</Textbox>>
